[ann]
 <i>Incredible!</i>

00:00:13.213 --> 00:00:16.116 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa rejects the goal by</i>
 <i>defending it with his face.</i>

00:00:16.149 --> 00:00:17.652 position:27% line:83% align:start
The ball is still
in play, guys.

00:00:17.685 --> 00:00:18.786 position:24% line:89% align:start
Get the ball back!

00:00:19.821 --> 00:00:20.755 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:00:20.788 --> 00:00:22.657 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
 <i>Tsubasa Ozora...</i>

00:00:22.690 --> 00:00:24.124 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu's genius...</i>

00:00:25.292 --> 00:00:28.563 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Without Wakabayashi</i>
 <i>and Misaki alongside you...</i>

00:00:28.596 --> 00:00:30.765 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>you still overcame</i>
 <i>every obstacle in your way,</i>

00:00:30.798 --> 00:00:34.002 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>without worrying about</i>
 <i>your opponent's strength.</i>

00:00:34.034 --> 00:00:35.570 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>How incredible.</i>

00:00:35.603 --> 00:00:38.205 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I faced you with</i>
 <i>all of my aggression,</i>

00:00:38.238 --> 00:00:40.542 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>with all of</i>
 <i>my body's strength,</i>

00:00:40.575 --> 00:00:44.344 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>and with all of my teammates</i>
 <i>support as well.</i>

00:00:44.378 --> 00:00:46.614 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even with all that</i>
 <i>in my favor...</i>

00:00:46.648 --> 00:00:49.984 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>it's impossible to</i>
 <i>defeat you on the pitch.</i>

00:00:50.018 --> 00:00:51.819 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:00:51.853 --> 00:00:53.287 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Sanae]
Don't get up again.

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.321 position:38% line:89% align:start
Please...

00:00:55.557 --> 00:00:56.524 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's go ahead, guys!

00:00:57.457 --> 00:00:59.226 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Nankatsu gets</i>
 <i>the ball back.</i>

00:00:59.259 --> 00:01:01.663 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's the second half</i>
 <i>of the extra time.</i>

00:01:01.696 --> 00:01:03.031 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>There's five minutes left.</i>

00:01:03.063 --> 00:01:05.733 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Both teams have given</i>
 <i>their all on the pitch.</i>

00:01:05.767 --> 00:01:06.634 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>The referee's</i>

00:01:06.668 --> 00:01:08.435 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>taking a look at his watch.</i>
-[groan]

00:01:08.468 --> 00:01:09.771 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[panting]
-[Kojiro] <i>There's</i>

00:01:09.804 --> 00:01:12.707 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>no one else I want to beat</i>
 <i>more than you, Tsubasa.</i>

00:01:14.341 --> 00:01:15.242 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why?</i>

00:01:15.275 --> 00:01:16.678 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why can't I achieve it?</i>

00:01:17.612 --> 00:01:20.715 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>What do I have to do</i>
 <i>to surpass you?</i>

00:01:20.748 --> 00:01:22.249 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
 <i>How Tsubasa?</i>

00:01:22.282 --> 00:01:24.418 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>How can I be better</i>
 <i>than you?</i>

00:03:08.388 --> 00:03:09.724 position:24% line:77% align:start
-[narr] <i>Episode 52:</i>
-[ann] <i>They are</i>

00:03:09.757 --> 00:03:11.626 position:27% line:77% align:start
 <i>-Endless Dream.</i>
 <i>-only up by one goal.</i>

00:03:11.659 --> 00:03:13.193 position:30% line:77% align:start
 <i>Will Tsubasa's</i>
 <i>miraculous goal</i>

00:03:13.226 --> 00:03:15.663 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>be enough to give</i>
 <i>his team the championship?</i>

00:03:15.697 --> 00:03:16.363 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, the match

00:03:16.396 --> 00:03:17.397 position:27% line:83% align:start
-is almost over.
-[grunt]

00:03:17.431 --> 00:03:18.833 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hang in there until the end.

00:03:18.866 --> 00:03:20.034 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:03:20.068 --> 00:03:21.636 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>been able to come back</i>

00:03:21.669 --> 00:03:23.705 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>from inconceivable</i>
 <i>deficits.</i>

00:03:26.708 --> 00:03:29.077 position:16% line:83% align:start
Listen, let's finish this
once and for all.

00:03:29.110 --> 00:03:30.144 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>The white jerseys</i>

00:03:30.178 --> 00:03:31.445 position:21% line:83% align:start
- <i>look very confident</i>
-[grunt]

00:03:31.478 --> 00:03:32.580 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>in the second half against</i>
-[yelling]

00:03:32.613 --> 00:03:34.347 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>their toughest</i>
 <i>opponents yet.</i>

00:03:34.381 --> 00:03:35.650 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[gasps]

00:03:35.683 --> 00:03:38.686 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Darn it all.
-We can't take it from 'em.

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:39.854 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Not again...</i>

00:03:39.887 --> 00:03:41.589 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>We aren't losing again.</i>

00:03:41.622 --> 00:03:44.592 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can't lose to him</i>
 <i>one more time!</i>

00:03:44.625 --> 00:03:45.993 position:21% line:83% align:start
-What's wrong, Hyuga?
-Huh?

00:03:46.027 --> 00:03:47.562 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Get moving!
-Matsuyama!

00:03:47.595 --> 00:03:49.097 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
You're just standing there

00:03:49.130 --> 00:03:49.764 position:30% line:89% align:start
doing nothing!

00:03:50.665 --> 00:03:53.134 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>If I can't reach you,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa...</i>

00:03:53.167 --> 00:03:56.070 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll just have to show you</i>
 <i>my true self.</i>

00:03:56.104 --> 00:03:57.739 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll finish this match,</i>

00:03:57.772 --> 00:04:01.042 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>playing like I've done</i>
 <i>my whole life.</i>

00:04:01.075 --> 00:04:02.309 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:04:02.342 --> 00:04:04.311 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Hyuga desperately</i>
 <i>runs after the ball,</i>

00:04:04.344 --> 00:04:05.680 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>but it's useless.</i>
-[grunt]

00:04:05.713 --> 00:04:07.380 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>His speed isn't enough</i>
-[gasp]

00:04:07.414 --> 00:04:09.316 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>to catch up to Nankatsu.</i>
-[grunt]

00:04:09.349 --> 00:04:10.651 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Katagiri]
 <i>It's a shame.</i>

00:04:10.685 --> 00:04:12.553 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>He can't go head to head</i>
 <i>with Tsubasa.</i>

00:04:12.587 --> 00:04:14.421 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[grunt] [gasp]

00:04:14.454 --> 00:04:15.923 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[growl]
-[pant]

00:04:15.957 --> 00:04:17.959 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:04:17.992 --> 00:04:20.094 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Captain Hyuga...
-Captain...

00:04:20.128 --> 00:04:21.195 position:27% line:83% align:start
-We need to win.
-Hmm...

00:04:21.229 --> 00:04:22.897 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[yells]
-[ann] <i>Bolstered by Hyuga,</i>

00:04:22.930 --> 00:04:24.799 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>all of Toho advances.</i>

00:04:24.832 --> 00:04:25.767 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[yell]
-[gasp]

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:27.702 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Sorimachi's</i>
 <i>able to get the ball.</i>

00:04:27.735 --> 00:04:29.670 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Everyone...
-[Yutaka] Captain!

00:04:29.704 --> 00:04:30.671 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:31.706 --> 00:04:32.707 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you!

00:04:33.574 --> 00:04:34.208 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:04:34.242 --> 00:04:35.777 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll use my style of play.</i>

00:04:35.810 --> 00:04:38.846 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's the only thing
that can defeat Tsubasa.

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:40.014 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[ann] <i>One more attack</i>
-Come on, Toho!

00:04:40.047 --> 00:04:41.314 position:33% line:83% align:start
- <i>from Toho.</i>
-You can do it!

00:04:41.348 --> 00:04:43.117 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>There's only three minutes</i>
-You're here to win!

00:04:43.151 --> 00:04:44.417 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>on the clock.</i>

00:04:44.451 --> 00:04:45.318 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
[pant]

00:04:45.352 --> 00:04:46.954 position:30% line:83% align:start
We're going to
give it our all.

00:04:46.988 --> 00:04:48.756 position:27% line:83% align:start
Toho can't afford
to lose today.

00:04:48.790 --> 00:04:49.757 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:04:49.791 --> 00:04:50.858 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:04:50.892 --> 00:04:51.659 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>This is our last duel.</i>

00:04:52.827 --> 00:04:55.930 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>All of Nankatsu</i>
 <i>is coming back to defend.</i>

00:04:55.963 --> 00:04:56.531 position:44% line:89% align:start
Now!

00:04:56.564 --> 00:04:57.598 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:04:57.632 --> 00:05:00.635 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Hyuga faces Taki</i>
 <i>with incredible power!</i>

00:05:00.668 --> 00:05:02.302 position:19% line:83% align:start
We have to prevent them
from tying.

00:05:02.335 --> 00:05:03.538 position:30% line:89% align:start
Take the ball.

00:05:03.571 --> 00:05:04.272 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:05:04.304 --> 00:05:05.673 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[grunting]
-[ann] <i>Oh boy!</i>

00:05:05.706 --> 00:05:07.208 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>What a beautiful</i>
 <i>one-two pass from Toho.</i>

00:05:07.241 --> 00:05:09.076 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Here I go!
-We won't let you through!

00:05:09.110 --> 00:05:10.978 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[panting]
-I'm open!

00:05:11.012 --> 00:05:12.113 position:38% line:89% align:start
Takeshi!

00:05:12.146 --> 00:05:13.915 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And another</i>
 <i>one-two pass.</i>

00:05:13.948 --> 00:05:14.715 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>This time, it's between</i>

00:05:14.749 --> 00:05:16.449 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>Hyuga and Sawada.</i>
-[panting]

00:05:16.483 --> 00:05:18.252 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Hyuga's in front of</i>
 <i>the danger zone.</i>

00:05:18.286 --> 00:05:19.520 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>This is his chance.</i>

00:05:19.554 --> 00:05:20.387 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>With three minutes</i>

00:05:20.420 --> 00:05:21.155 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>on the clock,</i>
-[gasps]

00:05:21.189 --> 00:05:22.355 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Toho has another</i>

00:05:22.389 --> 00:05:23.891 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>chance to score.</i>
-[growl]

00:05:23.925 --> 00:05:26.794 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:05:26.828 --> 00:05:28.461 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tiger growl]

00:05:28.495 --> 00:05:29.931 position:19% line:89% align:start
You won't score, Hyuga!

00:05:29.964 --> 00:05:32.266 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're going to keep
Tsubasa's goal lead.

00:05:32.300 --> 00:05:33.568 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
[gasp]

00:05:33.601 --> 00:05:35.803 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>They formed a wall</i>
 <i>to stop me.</i>

00:05:36.871 --> 00:05:38.039 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Good, Nankatsu.</i>

00:05:38.906 --> 00:05:39.974 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa...</i>

00:05:40.007 --> 00:05:41.509 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>I lost again.</i>

00:05:41.542 --> 00:05:42.743 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>My soccer can't beat you...</i>

00:05:43.978 --> 00:05:47.882 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>but I don't care if I fall</i>
 <i>to you for one last time.</i>

00:05:47.915 --> 00:05:51.319 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>My soccer style is power.</i>
 <i>You'll see!</i>

00:05:51.384 --> 00:05:52.720 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll destroy that wall</i>

00:05:52.753 --> 00:05:54.922 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and destroy you</i>
 <i>while I'm at it.</i>

00:05:54.956 --> 00:05:56.824 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>All of my family's effort,</i>

00:05:56.858 --> 00:06:00.795 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and my teammates effort</i>
 <i>is in my next shot.</i>

00:06:00.828 --> 00:06:01.963 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Here I go!</i>

00:06:01.996 --> 00:06:03.965 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>This is my Tiger Shot!</i>

00:06:03.998 --> 00:06:05.266 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:06:05.299 --> 00:06:06.534 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't do it, Captain.

00:06:06.567 --> 00:06:08.368 position:13% line:83% align:start
You won't be able to score
like that.

00:06:08.401 --> 00:06:10.671 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-Wait up, Captain!

00:06:13.307 --> 00:06:15.009 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasp]
 <i>Takeshi!</i>

00:06:15.943 --> 00:06:17.211 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
No!

00:06:17.245 --> 00:06:20.314 position:16% line:83% align:start
Takeshi, lift your leg up
so I can use it!

00:06:20.348 --> 00:06:21.582 position:41% line:89% align:start
My leg?

00:06:21.616 --> 00:06:22.550 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[yell]
-[ann] <i>What?</i>

00:06:22.583 --> 00:06:23.918 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>What's happening?</i>

00:06:23.951 --> 00:06:25.887 position:35% line:83% align:start
You got it.
[grunt]

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.088 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:06:27.121 --> 00:06:28.122 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Hyuga piggybacked</i>

00:06:28.155 --> 00:06:29.190 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>off Sawada's leg</i>
-[yell]

00:06:29.223 --> 00:06:30.024 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>like a trampoline.</i>

00:06:30.057 --> 00:06:31.759 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-Impossible...

00:06:31.792 --> 00:06:32.760 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's he doing?

00:06:32.793 --> 00:06:33.928 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:33.961 --> 00:06:34.929 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:06:35.863 --> 00:06:36.931 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hyuga!
-Captain!

00:06:36.964 --> 00:06:38.532 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Kojiro!
-Big Brother!

00:06:39.533 --> 00:06:42.603 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Just like your style</i>
 <i>of play, Tsubasa?</i>

00:06:42.637 --> 00:06:45.072 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>No, this is real soccer.</i>

00:06:45.973 --> 00:06:47.642 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[tiger growl]

00:06:48.743 --> 00:06:51.545 position:33% line:83% align:start
Attack them,
and show them all...

00:06:51.579 --> 00:06:54.215 position:16% line:89% align:start
the Overhead Tiger Shot!

00:06:54.248 --> 00:06:56.517 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>A definitive shot</i>
 <i>from Hyuga towards the goal!</i>

00:06:56.550 --> 00:06:57.450 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-Incredible.

00:06:58.619 --> 00:07:01.756 position:13% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The ball's traveling</i>
 <i>like a gust of wind!</i>

00:07:01.789 --> 00:07:02.690 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:07:02.723 --> 00:07:04.258 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[ann] <i>The keeper Morisaki</i>
-[gasps]

00:07:04.292 --> 00:07:04.992 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>receives it with his body.</i>

00:07:05.026 --> 00:07:06.060 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:07:06.093 --> 00:07:09.030 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Morisaki's getting</i>
 <i>pushed towards the goal.</i>

00:07:09.063 --> 00:07:09.997 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:07:10.031 --> 00:07:10.965 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa!

00:07:12.066 --> 00:07:14.735 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Captain Tsubasa</i>
 <i>is able to get Morisaki.</i>

00:07:14.769 --> 00:07:16.570 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Looks like</i>
 <i>this'll be Nankatsu's</i>

00:07:16.604 --> 00:07:17.939 position:21% line:83% align:start
- <i>third championship.</i>
-[gasps]

00:07:17.972 --> 00:07:18.973 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:07:19.740 --> 00:07:20.675 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:20.708 --> 00:07:21.943 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:07:21.976 --> 00:07:22.977 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:26.881 --> 00:07:29.317 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>The ball is inside!</i>

00:07:29.350 --> 00:07:30.685 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Toho Academy managed</i>

00:07:30.718 --> 00:07:31.986 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>to tie the match!</i>
-[cheering]

00:07:32.019 --> 00:07:34.155 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's only one minute</i>
 <i>until the end,</i>

00:07:34.188 --> 00:07:36.524 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and Toho ties</i>
 <i>the scoreboard.</i>

00:07:36.557 --> 00:07:37.625 position:30% line:83% align:start
