I should head to.

00:14:49.890 --> 00:14:51.358 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well said, Hyuga.

00:14:51.392 --> 00:14:51.959 position:38% line:89% align:start
Grow up.

00:14:52.794 --> 00:14:54.629 position:27% line:83% align:start
