00:14:56.698 --> 00:14:57.898 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:14:59.099 --> 00:15:00.668 position:16% line:89% align:start
I think this is the end.

00:15:00.702 --> 00:15:03.437 position:27% line:83% align:start
Our rivalry ended
with today's match.

00:15:03.470 --> 00:15:04.572 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:15:04.606 --> 00:15:05.540 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

