00:17:43.196 --> 00:17:45.633 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yeah.
Of course you can, Misugi.

00:17:46.868 --> 00:17:47.769 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Good for him.</i>

00:17:48.736 --> 00:17:49.837 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-[narr] <i>Team Toho.</i>

00:17:49.871 --> 00:17:52.406 position:27% line:83% align:start
