 <i>Yeah...</i>

00:23:03.618 --> 00:23:05.987 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm happy to have</i>
 <i>been in Nankatsu.</i>

00:23:06.020 --> 00:23:07.288 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Three years ago,</i>

00:23:07.321 --> 00:23:10.124 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>my dream of going to Brazil</i>
 <i>with Roberto was derailed...</i>

00:23:11.592 --> 00:23:13.694 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>But thanks to that,</i>
 <i>I achieved another dream</i>

00:23:13.728 --> 00:23:16.130 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>next to my beloved</i>
 <i>teammates.</i>

00:23:16.163 --> 00:23:17.598 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Sao Paulo, Brazil.</i>

00:23:17.632 --> 00:23:18.900 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>But this time around,</i>

00:23:18.933 --> 00:23:20.368 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>I will go to Brazil,</i>

00:23:20.400 --> 00:23:22.703 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>the country of soccer.</i>

00:23:22.737 --> 00:23:27.008 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The country that made me</i>
 <i>fall in love with soccer.</i>

00:23:27.041 --> 00:23:28.109 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Finally...</i>

00:23:31.178 --> 00:23:34.148 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll go to South America</i>
 <i>to become a professional.</i>

00:23:36.317 --> 00:23:38.286 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Even if I achieved a dream,</i>

